cumulus (2.17.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Overflow issue fixed in HwInfo::getFreeUserSpace. Reported free disk space
    was wrong.
    
  * Do not reporting a landing, if IGC log file was not opened.
  
  * Home site name added to personal page.
  
  * If moving away from a violated airspace no longer alarms are generated, if
    movement is from inside, to very near, to near and out side.

  * If a task was set and the last taskpoint was selected, the arrival altitude
    display showed always zero.

  * Combo boxes for sky directions replaced against toggle buttons in coordinate
    editor. Makes the operation with fingers simpler as before.
    
  * Flarm IGC file download support added.
  
 -- Axel Pauli <kflog.cumulus@googlemail.com>  Thu, 14 Aug 2012 21:53:14 +0200

